org.matrix.androidsdk

Class MXDataHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matrix.androidsdk.MXDataHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMXEventListener

    public class MXDataHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMXEventListener
    The data handler provides a layer to help manage matrix input and output.
    • Handles events
    • Stores the data in its storage layer
    • Provides the means for an app to get callbacks for data changes
